nt the best!<\/span><\/h5>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"h-text h-text-component style-188 style-local-6-c7 position-relative h-element\" data-colibri-id=\"6-c7\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<p>Looking for professional classic portraits in Hampshire or Basingstoke? Peter Farrar creates high quality portrait photography for individuals, families, professionals, performers and businesses throughout Hampshire.<\/p>\n<p>Whether you require studio portraits, location photography, professional headshots or personal branding images, every session is tailored to capture your personality and create lasting images.<\/p>\n<p>Based in Basingstoke, Hampshire, Peter brings decades of photographic experience and a relaxed approach that helps clients feel comfortable in front of the camera. The result is natural, professional portraits that you will be proud to display and share.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"content\" class=\"h-section h-section-global-spacing d-flex align-items-lg-center align-items-md-center align-items-center style-201 style-local-6-c9 position-relative\" data-colibri-component=\"section\" data-colibri-id=\"6-c9\">\n<div class=\"h-section-grid-container h-section-fluid-container\">\n<div class=\"h-row-container gutters-row-lg-0 gutters-row-md-0 gutters-row-2 gutters-row-v-lg-0 gutters-row-v-md-0 gutters-row-v-2 style-202 style-local-6-c10 position-relative\" data-colibri-id=\"6-c10\">\n<div class=\"h-row justify-content-lg-center justify-content-md-center justify-content-center align-items-lg-stretch align-items-md-stretch align-items-stretch gutters-col-lg-0 gutters-col-md-0 gutters-col-2 gutters-col-v-lg-0 gutters-col-v-md-0 gutters-col-v-2\">\n<div class=\"h-column h-column-container d-flex h-col-lg-auto h-col-md-auto h-col-auto style-203-outer style-local-6-c11-outer\">\n<div class=\"d-flex h-flex-basis h-column__inner h-px-lg-0 h-px-md-0 h-px-0 v-inner-lg-0 v-inner-md-0 v-inner-0 style-203 style-